## Task 3: Update HTML template in index.astro
**File:** `src/pages/en/index.astro` lines 200–229
**Change:** Replace the section HTML to:
- Add intro paragraphs in a `body-text` div (existing pattern used elsewhere on the page)
- Cards now render `card.title` as `<h3>` + `card.description` as `<p>`
- Closing text from i18n instead of hardcoded
- CTABox receives explicit props from i18n

```astro
<!-- Why Aunova Section -->
<section class="why-aunova" id="why-aunova">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-content">
      <h2 class="section-title">{t.whyAunova.title}</h2>
      <div class="body-text">
        {t.whyAunova.intro.map((paragraph) => <p>{paragraph}</p>)}
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="stacked-cards">
      {t.whyAunova.cards.map((card, index) => {
        const Icon = whyIcons[index];
        return (
          <div class="stacked-card">
            <div class="stacked-card-circle">
              <Icon size={22} />
            </div>
            <div class="stacked-card-text">
              <h3 class="stacked-card-title">{card.title}</h3>
              <p>{card.description}</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        );
      })}
    </div>

    <p class="why-closing">
      {t.whyAunova.closing}
    </p>

    <CTABox
      title={t.whyAunova.cta.title}
      description={t.whyAunova.cta.description}
      buttonText={t.whyAunova.cta.button}
      buttonLink={`/${lang}/contact`}
    />
  </div>
</section>
```

